inputs.name: example-aws-profile-role-ed20ee7c
inputs.templateBody:
AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
                Outputs:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup
                Resources:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup
                        Properties:
                          DesiredCapacity: 2
                          LaunchConfigurationName: example-aws-profile-role-nodeLaunchConfiguration-4b4641a
                          MinSize: 1
                          MaxSize: 2
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-03c2da794b62e62ef","subnet-0ecd0851125a47ae9","subnet-0d825b95e0132b3d9"]
                          Tags:
                          
                          - Key: Name
                            Value: example-aws-profile-role-eksCluster-b107de2-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/example-aws-profile-role-eksCluster-b107de2
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '1'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
